'''2015年古爾達斯普爾恐怖攻擊事件'''，是指發生於2015年7月27日，在[[印度|印度]][[旁遮普地区|旁遮普地区]][[古尔达斯普尔县|古尔达斯普尔县]][[迪纳纳加尔|迪纳纳加尔]]鎮的一起恐怖攻擊事件。至少四名武裝槍手在一輛[[公共汽車|公共汽車]]上開槍，接著襲擊了當地的一處[[警察局|警察局]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tribuneindia.com/news/punjab/terror-attack-in-gurdaspur-8-dead-4-injured/111963.html|title=Terror attack in Gurdaspur; police SP among 12 dead|author=Tribune News Service|work=http://www.tribuneindia.com/news/punjab/terror-attack-in-gurdaspur-8-dead-4-injured/111963.html|accessdate=27 July 2015|archive-date=2015-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150727101202/http://www.tribuneindia.com/news/punjab/terror-attack-in-gurdaspur-8-dead-4-injured/111963.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/other-states/gunmen-attack-punjabs-gurdaspur/article7469246.ece?homepage=true AN AUDACIOUS STRIKE] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/other-states/gunmen-attack-punjabs-gurdaspur/article7469246.ece?homepage=true |date=20190121023933 }}, [[Frontline_(magazine)|Frontline (magazine)]], 2015-7-27</ref>。本起攻擊造成至少6死9傷，而傷亡人數可能還要再增加<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tribuneindia.com/news/punjab/terror-attack-in-gurdaspur-9-dead-4-injured/111963.html|title=Terror attack in Gurdaspur; police SP among 12 dead|author=Tribune News Service|work=http://www.tribuneindia.com/news/punjab/terror-attack-in-gurdaspur-9-dead-4-injured/111963.html|accessdate=27 July 2015|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224181143/https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/punjab/terror-attack-in-gurdaspur-9-dead-4-injured/111963.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

